<script>
$().ready(function() {
var clipboard = new ClipboardJS('.urlCopy>button', {
text: function() {
return fn_getUrl();
}
});
clipboard.on('success', function(e) {
alert("URL이 복사되었습니다.");
});
clipboard.on('error', function(e) {
alert("URL복사에 실패했습니다.");
});
$("#copyUrl").val(fn_getUrl());
});

function fn_getUrl(){
var rtnUrl = "";
var url = decodeURIComponent(location.href);
url = decodeURIComponent(url).replace("#","");
url = decodeURIComponent(url).replace(";","");
rtnUrl = url.replace("#;","");
return rtnUrl;
}
function shareSns(sns){
var snsTitle = '';
var snsItems = new Array();
var winOpt = new Array();
var snsUrl = fn_getUrl();
snsItems['facebook'] = "http://www.facebook.com/share.php?t="+encodeURIComponent(snsTitle) + "&u=" + encodeURIComponent(snsUrl);
snsItems['twitter'] = "https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=" + encodeURIComponent(snsTitle + "\n" + snsUrl);
snsItems['kakao'] = "https://story.kakao.com/share?url="+encodeURIComponent(snsUrl);
snsItems['blog'] = "http://blog.naver.com/openapi/share?url="+encodeURIComponent(snsUrl)+"&title="+encodeURIComponent(snsTitle);
winOpt['facebook'] = "width=700, height=500, resizable=yes";
winOpt['twitter'] = "width=700, height=500, resizable=yes";
winOpt['kakao'] = "width=500, height=500, resizable=yes";
winOpt['blog'] = "width=500, height=500, resizeable=yes";
var win = window.open(snsItems[sns], sns, winOpt[sns]);
if (win) {
win.focus();
}
}
</script>

var gnbDep1 = 0;

//mySheet.SetSheetWidth(500);
window.print();

$(window).on("resize", function(){
if(window.innerWidth<=1600){
$("#contents").removeClass("open-left-menu");
$(".btn-left").removeClass("open");
$("#lnb").css("display", "none");
}
if(window.innerWidth>1600){
$("#contents").removeClass("open-left-menu");
$(".btn-left").removeClass("open");
$("#lnb").css("display", "block");
}
});

$(function(){
$("#btnLeft").bind("click", function(){

if(window.innerWidth<=1600 && window.innerWidth>1024){
var leftDisplay = $("#lnb").css("display");
var ctntClassName = "open-left-menu";
if(leftDisplay == "none"){
$("#contents").addClass(ctntClassName);
$(".btn-left").addClass("open");
}else {
$("#contents").removeClass(ctntClassName);
$(".btn-left").removeClass("open");
}
$("#lnb").toggle();
}
});
});

function fn_save_opinion(){
if($('#satisForm input:radio[name=SCO]:checked').length < 1){
alert('Select the satisfaction score.');
return;
}
if($('#satisForm [name=OPINION]').val().trim() == ''){
alert('Enter your comment.');
return;
}
if(!confirm('Add your comment on satisfaction?')){
return;
}
fn_comm_ajax({
url : "/ajaxf/frSatisSvc/saveSatis.do",
data : $("#satisForm").serialize(),
dataType : "json",
success : function(data) {
alert(data.MSG);
if(data.RESULT == 1){
location.reload();
}
}
});
}
</script>

<script>

var touchStartX;
var touchStartY;
var touchEndX;
var touchEndY;
$(function(){
/*
22.07.22
터치 이벤트 클릭을 전환(ibsheet 내에 이벤트성 태그만 선적용, 이외 태그 추가 가능성 있음)
*/
var clickEvent = (function() {
if ('ontouchend' in document.documentElement === true) {
$(document).on('touchstart', '[class*=GridMain] .btn-download, [class*=GridMain] .btn-search, [class*=GridMain] .btn-fav-sheet, [class*=GridMain] .btn.grid.inquiry', function(e){
touchStartX = e.originalEvent.touches[0].pageX;
touchStartY = e.originalEvent.touches[0].pageY;
});
$(document).on('touchend', '[class*=GridMain] .btn-download, [class*=GridMain] .btn-search, [class*=GridMain] .btn-fav-sheet, [class*=GridMain] .btn.grid.inquiry', function(e){
touchEndX = e.originalEvent.changedTouches[0].pageX;
touchEndY = e.originalEvent.changedTouches[0].pageY;
var touchX = touchEndX - touchStartX;
var touchY = touchEndY - touchStartY;
if(Math.abs(touchX) <= 5 && Math.abs(touchY) <= 5){
e.preventDefault();
$(this).trigger('click');
}
});
}
})();
$(document).on("click", ".btn_topSearch", function(){
var ifrSrc = "/search/searchPop.do";
$('<iframe id="iframeSearchPop" class="pop_iframe on" src="'+ifrSrc+'" frameborder="0" style="left: 0;border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; top: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; position: absolute; z-index: 999999;"/>').appendTo($("body"));
});

});

$(function(){
$(document).on("click", "button.btn-fav.btnBookmark", function(event){
var bookmark_obj = $(this);
if(!$(bookmark_obj).hasClass("active")){
fn_comm_ajax({
asyc : false,
url : "/ajaxf/frMyportfolioSvc/insertBookMark.do",
data : $("#bookmarkForm").serialize(),
dataType : "json",
success : function(data){
if(data != null){
if(data.RESULT == 1){
$('.noti-layer.fav > div > span').text(data.MSG);
$('.noti-layer.fav').hide().show().delay(1500).fadeOut(100);
$(bookmark_obj).addClass("active")
return false;
}else{
$('.noti-layer.fav > div > span').text(data.MSG);
$('.noti-layer.fav').hide().show().delay(1500).fadeOut(100);
$(bookmark_obj).removeClass("active");
return false;
}
}else{
$('.noti-layer.fav > div > span').text("처리에 실패 하였습니다.\n관리자에게 문의 해주세요.");
$('.noti-layer.fav').hide().show().delay(1500).fadeOut(100);
$(bookmark_obj).removeClass("active");
return false;
}
}
});
}else{
fn_comm_ajax({
asyc : false,
url : "/ajaxf/frMyportfolioSvc/deleteBookMark.do",
data : $("#bookmarkForm").serialize(),
dataType : "json",
success : function(data){
if(data != null){
if(data.RESULT == 1){

// 검색구분 선택
$(document).on("click", "#sub_total_search ul.dropdown-menu li a", function(){
$("#sub_total_search button.dropdown-toggle").text($(this).text());
$("#sub_total_search ul.dropdown-menu li a").removeClass("active");
$(this).addClass("active");
$("#totalSearchForm input[name=t]").val($(this).data("searchtab"));
});
// 검색어 순위 선택
$(document).on("click", "#sub_total_search .keyword-ranking div.carousel-item a", function(){
var search_txt = $.trim($(this).find("span:not(.num)").eq(0).text());
$("#totalSearchForm input[name=q]").val(search_txt);
//특수문자,공백 체크
//if(Chk_word(search_txt)) return;
$("#totalSearchForm").attr("action","/totalSearch.do");
$("#totalSearchForm").submit();
});
});

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : goSearch
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.08.13
* 3. 작성자 : 이해규
* 5. 설명 : 통합검색 화면 이동
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.08.13-이해규-작성
* </pre>
*/
function goSearch() {
if($.trim($("#totalSearchForm input[name=q]").val())==''){
alert("검색어를 입력해주세요.");
return false;
}
var search_txt = $.trim($("#totalSearchForm input[name=q]").val());
$("#totalSearchForm input[name=q]").val(search_txt);
//특수문자,공백 체크
//if(Chk_word(search_txt)) return;
$("#totalSearchForm").attr("action","/totalSearch.do");
$("#totalSearchForm").submit();
}

function Chk_word(word){
var re = /[~!@#?{}$%^&*|`\()\-=+<>_';:",.]/gi;
if(re.test(word) && word.trim()!=''){
alert("특수문자는 입력하실수 없습니다.");
word = word.replace(re,"");
$("#totalSearchForm input[name=q]").val(word);
return true;
}
return false;
}

</script>

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_search
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.10
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : 업체명, 법인/사업자번호 검색
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.10-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_search(opCode){
if(opCode == 1){
if($("#COMNM").val() == ""){
$.alert("업체명을 입력해주세요.");
$("#COMNM").focus();
return;
}
fn_replaceLs($("#COMNM").get(0), $("#ENGLS_YN").get(0));
//(주) 구문 제거
fn_companyNameChange($("#COMNM").get(0));
if($("#tabIdx").val() == ''){
$("#tabIdx").val("1");
}
$("#COMP_CD").val("");
$("#CRPNO").val("");
$("#SEARCH_TYPE").val("2");
} else if(opCode == 2){
if($("#CRPNO").val() == ""){
$.alert("법인번호 또는 사업자번호를 입력해주세요.");
$("#CRPNO").focus();
return;
}
$("#CRPNO").val().replace(/-/g, '');
if($("#tabIdx").val() == ''){
$("#tabIdx").val("1");
}
$("#COMNM").val("");
$("#SEARCH_TYPE").val("3");
}
$("#sendForm").attr("action", "/cms/frDisclosureCon/compSearchResult.do");
$("#sendForm").submit();
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_compView
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 회사 Overview 화면 이동
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_compView(compCd){
$("#sendForm [name=COMP_CD]").val(compCd);
location.href = "/cms/compDetail/topUtilLink.do?"+$("#sendForm").serialize();
}
</script>

<script>
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : searchEnterkey
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.16
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 엔터 키 감지 시 검색버튼 클릭 이벤트 발생
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.16-비브이에스-작성
* </pre>
*/
function searchEnterkey() {
if (window.event.keyCode == 13) {
fn_search(1);
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : searchEnterkey2
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.16
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 엔터 키 감지 시 검색버튼 클릭 이벤트 발생
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.16-비브이에스-작성
* </pre>
*/
function searchEnterkey2() {
if (window.event.keyCode == 13) {
fn_search(2);
}
}
</script>

/**

* 1. 함수명 : fn_tab1ExcelDown

* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.24-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/

var extParma_tab1;
function fn_tab1ExcelDown(extendParam){
var dt = timestampFormat(new Date().getTime(), '%Y%M%D%H%I%S');
extParma_tab1 = extendParam;
var firstSheetObj;
var firstYn = false;
if('true' == 'true' || '' == 'true' || '' == 'true'){

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet9_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.06
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(최근평정내역 및 최근Full보고서)데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.06-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet9_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_VALD_YN == "N"){
jsonObj.Data[idx]["FontColor"] = "#A0A0A0";
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != null && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != '-' && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != ''){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download pdf" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"03"+'\', \'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'m4R0rUAW4REnW0XPhHfDCw==\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-pdf.png" alt="평가의견 다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].FNAF_BRF_FILE_NM != null && jsonObj.Data[idx].FNAF_BRF_FILE_NM != '-' && jsonObj.Data[idx].FNAF_BRF_FILE_NM != ''){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download excel" onclick="fn_finExcel(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].FNAF_BRF_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-excel.png" alt="재무요약 다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].FNAF_BRF_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD != null && jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD != "" ){
var fileGbn = "";
var cancel = "";
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '01') fileGbn = "F";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '03') fileGbn = "S";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '04') fileGbn = "U";
else{
cancel = "canceled";
}
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download report '+ cancel +'" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"01"+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].encFileNm0+'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'m4R0rUAW4REnW0XPhHfDCw==\');">' + fileGbn + '</button>';

jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
}
}
}

return jsonObj;
}

/**

function mySheet10_OnClick(Row, Col, Value, CellX, CellY, CellW, CellH){
if(Row == 0){
return;
}

var rowData = mySheet10.GetRowData(Row);
if(saveNm == "RSRCH_TITL"){
fn_rschDetail(rowData.RSRCH_RPT_ID, rowData.DOC_MNG_NO, rowData.DTA_SEQNO, rowData.RSRCH_TYCD, '', '', rowData.FILE_XTNS);
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet10_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.06
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(관련리서치(Overview))데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.06-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet10_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var myRschYn = '';
if(myRschArr.includes(jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID)){
myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}else{
myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}
jsonObj.Data[idx].MY_RSCH_YN = myRschYn;
var fileXtns = jsonObj.Data[idx].FILE_XTNS;
if('' != fileXtns && typeof fileXtns != "undefined") fileXtns = fileXtns.toLowerCase();
if(null != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO && '' != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != '' && typeof jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != "undefined"){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download '+fileXtns+'" onclick="fn_krrchDown(\''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DTA_SEQNO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'\', \'\', \'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-'+fileXtns+'.png" alt="다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].DOWN_ICON = obj;
}
jsonObj.Data[idx]["RSRCH_TITL#FontColor"] = "#105DA9";
}
}
}
return jsonObj;
}

myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}else{
myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}
jsonObj.Data[idx].MY_RSCH_YN = myRschYn;
var fileXtns = jsonObj.Data[idx].FILE_XTNS;
if('' != fileXtns && typeof fileXtns != "undefined") fileXtns = fileXtns.toLowerCase();
if(null != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO && '' != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != '' && typeof jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != "undefined"){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download '+fileXtns+'" onclick="fn_krrchDown(\''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DTA_SEQNO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'\', \'\', \'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-'+fileXtns+'.png" alt="다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].DOWN_ICON = obj;
}
jsonObj.Data[idx]["RSRCH_TITL#FontColor"] = "#105DA9";
}
}
}
return jsonObj;
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_setXData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.27
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : x축 데이터 설정
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.27-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_setXData(param){
var x_data = [];
var json_data = JSON.parse(param);
if(json_data != null){
for(var i=0; i<json_data.length; i++){
x_data.push(json_data[i]);
}
}
return x_data;

}
function fn_setYData(param){
var y_data = [];
var json_data = JSON.parse(param);
if(json_data != null){
for(var i=0; i<json_data.length; i++){
y_data.push(json_data[i]);
}
}
return y_data;

}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_plotSetting
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.27
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 표시되는 Y축등급명/Y축값 설정
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.27-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_plotSetting(param){
var obj = JSON.parse(param);
var len = 0;
len = Object.keys(obj).length;

var cnt = 0;
var str = '';
$.each(obj, function(key, value){
str += '{"value": '+value+',"color": "#b5b7b9","dashStyle": "ShortDot","width": 0.7,"label": {"align": "left","text": "'+key
+'","Style": {"Color":"#7F7F7F","FontSize":"13px"},"X": -30, "Y": 5}}';
cnt++;
if(cnt!=len){
str += ",";
}
});

var jObj = JSON.parse("[" + str + "]");

return jObj;
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_plotSetting2
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.27
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : X축 기준라인 데이터(세로선, 날짜) 설정
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.27-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_plotSetting2(param){
var str = '';
var list = $.parseJSON(param);
var len = list.length;
for(var i=0; i<len; i++){
str += "{\"color\": \"#7F7F7F\",\"value\": " + list[i].value + ",\"dashStyle\": \"ShortDot\",\"width\": 0.7,"
+ "\"label\": {\"verticalAlign\": \"bottom\",\"align\": \"center\",\"text\": " + list[i].basisDate + ","
+ "\"Style\": {\"color\":\"#7F7F7F\",\"FontSize\":\"11px\"},\"rotation\": 0,\"X\": -4, \"Y\": 15}}";
if(i!=len-1){
str += ",";
}
}
var jObj = JSON.parse("[" + str + "]");

return jObj;
}

function mySheet1_OnBeforeSort(col){
var nm = mySheet1.ColSaveName(col);
fn_ibsheetHeaderSortImgInit(mySheet1);
if(nm == 'GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheet1, col, 'GRD', 'CUR_GRCD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'ISSUE_AMT_RESULT'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheet1, col, 'ISSUE_AMT_RESULT', 'ISSUE_AMT');
return false;
}
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet1_OnClick
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.31
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : 회사채 시트 클릭 이벤트
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.31-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet1_OnClick(Row, Col, Value, CellX, CellY, CellW, CellH){
if(Row == 0){
return;
}
var saveNm = mySheet1.ColSaveName(Col);
var rowData = mySheet1.GetRowData(Row);
if(saveNm == "BOND_NO"){
fn_subPage('01', rowData.SVC_ID, rowData.TRNC_NO);
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet1_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.09
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(회사채)데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.09-비브이에스-최초작성
* 2022.08.29-홍성학- 금액 '0.00' 은 '0' 으로 변환
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet1_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var isValidStr = jsonObj.Data[idx].isValid;
if(isValidStr.toUpperCase() == "N"){
jsonObj.Data[idx]["FontColor"] = "#A0A0A0";
jsonObj.Data[idx]["BOND_NO#FontColor"] = "#97b0c9";
}
// if(fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO) != "" && jsonObj.Data[idx].supYn1 == 'Y'){
// jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO = jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO + '*';
// }
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO = jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO + fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].COMP_GUAR_MARK);
if('000023' == '700073' && (jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO == '032-1' || jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO == '032-2')){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = "";
} else if('000023' == '700581' && jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NO == '051'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = "";
} else {
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT != '' && jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT != null){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD == null || fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD) == ""){
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_ICON = "";
} else {
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn grid btn-search" onclick="fn_viewBondSpec(\''+jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD+'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-search-big-dark.png" alt="채권발행정보 보기"/>';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_ICON = obj;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != null && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != '-' && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != ''){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download pdf" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"03"+'\', \'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-pdf.png" alt="평가의견 다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_EXIS_YN != 'N'){
var fileGbn = "";
var cancel = "";
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '01') fileGbn = "F";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '03') fileGbn = "S";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '04') fileGbn = "U";
else{
cancel = "canceled";
}
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download report '+ cancel +'" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"01"+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].encFileNm0+'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\');">' + fileGbn + '</button>';

jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
//ESG인증 여부
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_YN == 'Y'){
var esgBtn = '<button type="button" class="btn grid btn-esg" title="Summary Report" onclick="fn_openResearchPop(\'000023\');">ESG</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_ICON = esgBtn;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT != null){
//금액 '0.00' 은 '0' 으로 변환
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT == '0.00' || jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT == '0.0'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT = '0';
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '02'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = '$ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '03'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = '¥ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}else{
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}
}
}
}
}
return jsonObj;
}

* <pre>

function mySheet8_OnLoadData(data){

}

}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_EXIS_YN != 'N'){

var cancel = "";
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '01') fileGbn = "F";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '03') fileGbn = "S";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '04') fileGbn = "U";
else{
cancel = "canceled";
}
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download report '+ cancel +'" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"01"+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].encFileNm0+'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\');">' + fileGbn + '</button>';

jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
//ESG인증 여부
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_YN == 'Y'){
var esgBtn = '<button type="button" class="btn grid btn-esg" title="Summary Report" onclick="fn_openResearchPop(\'000023\');">ESG</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_ICON = esgBtn;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT != null){
//금액 '0.00' 은 '0' 으로 변환
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT == '0.00' || jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT == '0.0'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT = '0';
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '02'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = '$ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '03'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = '¥ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}else{
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}
}
}
}
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet2_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.09
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(기업어음)데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.09-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet2_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var isValidStr = jsonObj.Data[idx].isValid;
if(isValidStr.toUpperCase() == "N"){
jsonObj.Data[idx]["FontColor"] = "#A0A0A0";
}
if(fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_OGL) != "" && jsonObj.Data[idx].supYn1 == 'Y'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_OGL = jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_OGL + '*';
}
if(fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_ATAT) != "" && jsonObj.Data[idx].supYn2 == 'Y'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_ATAT = jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_ATAT + '*';
}
if(fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_PRDC) != "" && jsonObj.Data[idx].supYn3 == 'Y'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_PRDC = jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_PRDC + '*';
}
var gSeq = "";
if(gSeq > 0){
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CP_CNTS != '0'){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn grid btn-search" onclick="fn_viewCPList(\''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-search-big-dark.png" alt="발행내역 보기"/>';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].CP_RESULT = obj;
}
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != null && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != '-' && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != ''){

}

for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var isValidStr = jsonObj.Data[idx].isValid;
if(isValidStr.toUpperCase() == "N"){
jsonObj.Data[idx]["FontColor"] = "#A0A0A0";
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT != '' && jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT != null){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD == null || fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD) == ""){
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_ICON = "";
} else {
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn grid btn-search" onclick="fn_viewBondSpec(\''+jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD+'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-search-big-dark.png" alt="채권발행정보 보기"/>';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_ICON = obj;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != null && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != '-' && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != ''){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download pdf" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"03"+'\', \'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-pdf.png" alt="평가의견 다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_EXIS_YN != 'N'){
var fileGbn = "";
var cancel = "";
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '01') fileGbn = "F";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '03') fileGbn = "S";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '04') fileGbn = "U";
else{
cancel = "canceled";
}
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download report '+ cancel +'" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"01"+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].encFileNm0+'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\');">' + fileGbn + '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
//ESG인증 여부
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_YN == 'Y'){
var esgBtn = '<button type="button" class="btn grid btn-esg" title="Summary Report" onclick="fn_openResearchPop(\'000023\');">ESG</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_ICON = esgBtn;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT != null){
//금액 '0.00' 은 '0' 으로 변환
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT == '0.00' || jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT == '0.0'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT = '0';
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '02'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = '$ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '03'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = '¥ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}else{
jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT_RESULT = jsonObj.Data[idx].ISSUE_AMT;
}
}
}
}
}
return jsonObj;
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet6_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.10
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(유동화익스포져(CFR))데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.10-비브이에스-최초작성
* 2022.08.29-홍성학- 금액 '0.00' 은 '0' 으로 변환
* 2022.08.30-홍성학- 통화 단위 특수한 조건으로 포함
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet6_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_VALD_YN == "N"){
jsonObj.Data[idx]["FontColor"] = "#A0A0A0";
}
if('000023' == '802760' && jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NM == '시리즈C 제 1차'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NM_RESULT = '시리즈C';
} else if('000023' == '802760' && jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NM == '시리즈A 제2회차 기업어음'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NM_RESULT = '시리즈A';

} else {
jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NM_RESULT = jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_NM;
}
//통화 기호 구분
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT != '' && jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT != null){
if('000023' == '802895'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT_RESULT = '400';
jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT = '400';
} else if('000023' == '802964'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT_RESULT = '1,340';
jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT = '1,340';
} else {
//금액 '0.00' 은 '0' 으로 변환
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT == '0.00' || jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT == '0.0'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT = '0';
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '02'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT_RESULT = '$ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT;
}else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].CURR_CD == '03'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT_RESULT = '¥ ' + jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT;

jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT_RESULT = jsonObj.Data[idx].AGRE_AMT;

}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD == null || fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].BOND_STND_CD) == ""){

fn_subPage('10', rowData.SVC_ID, rowData.TRNC_NO);
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet3_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.10
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(기업신용평가(ICR))데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.10-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet3_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var isValidStr = jsonObj.Data[idx].isValid;
if(isValidStr.toUpperCase() == "N"){
jsonObj.Data[idx]["FontColor"] = "#A0A0A0";
}
if(fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_OGL) != "" && jsonObj.Data[idx].supYn1 == 'Y'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_OGL = jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_OGL + '*';
}
if(fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_ATAT) != "" && jsonObj.Data[idx].supYn2 == 'Y'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_ATAT = jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_ATAT + '*';
}
if(fn_strNullChk(jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_PRDC) != "" && jsonObj.Data[idx].supYn3 == 'Y'){
jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_PRDC = jsonObj.Data[idx].GRD_PRDC + '*';
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != null && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != '-' && jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM != ''){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download pdf" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"03"+'\', \'\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-pdf.png" alt="평가의견 다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].RTNG_OPN_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_EXIS_YN != 'N'){
var fileGbn = "";
var cancel = "";
if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '01') fileGbn = "F";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '03') fileGbn = "S";
else if(jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_TP_CD == '04') fileGbn = "U";
else{
cancel = "canceled";
}
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download report '+ cancel +'" onclick="fn_reportChk(\'000023\', \'원메가원창제일차(주)\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_NM+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].SVC_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].EVAL_SEQNO+'\', \''+"01"+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].encFileNm0+'\',\'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\', \'eye@FS.8GwJYS.V3.tfxBg==\', \'3xJQi2TwslfHECDe7X6Ewg==\');">' + fileGbn + '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].RPT_FILE_ICON = obj;
}
//ESG인증 여부
// if(jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_YN == 'Y'){
// var esgBtn = '<button type="button" class="btn grid btn-esg" title="Summary Report" onclick="fn_openResearchPop(\'000023\');">ESG</button>';
// jsonObj.Data[idx].ESG_ICON = esgBtn;
// }
}
}
}
return jsonObj;
}

* </pre>

function fn_openResearchPop(compCd){
$("body").css("overflow-y","hidden");
var ifrSrc = "/cms/frResearchCon/frEsgResearchRefCompPop.do?COMP_CD="+compCd;
$('<iframe id="iframeResearchPop" class="pop_iframe on" src="'+ifrSrc+'" frameborder="0" style="left: 0;border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; top: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100vh; position: fixed; z-index: 999999; backdrop-filter: blur(3px);"/>').appendTo($("body"));
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet10_1_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.06
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(관련리서치(리서치))데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.06-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet10_1_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var myRschYn = '';
if(myRschArr.includes(jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID)){
myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}else{
myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}
jsonObj.Data[idx].MY_RSCH_YN = myRschYn;
var fileXtns = jsonObj.Data[idx].FILE_XTNS;
if('' != fileXtns && typeof fileXtns != "undefined") fileXtns = fileXtns.toLowerCase();
if(null != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO && '' != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != '' && typeof jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != "undefined"){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download '+fileXtns+'" onclick="fn_krrchDown(\''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DTA_SEQNO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'\', \'\', \'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-'+fileXtns+'.png" alt="다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].DOWN_ICON = obj;
}
jsonObj.Data[idx]["RSRCH_TITL#FontColor"] = "#105DA9";
}
}
}
return jsonObj;
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet15_1_OnClick
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.31
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : 관련리서치(리서치) 시트 클릭 이벤트
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.31-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet15_1_OnClick(Row, Col, Value, CellX, CellY, CellW, CellH){
if(Row == 0){
return;
}
var saveNm = mySheet15_1.ColSaveName(Col);
var rowData = mySheet15_1.GetRowData(Row);
if(saveNm == "RSRCH_TITL"){
fn_rschDetail(rowData.RSRCH_RPT_ID, rowData.DOC_MNG_NO, rowData.DTA_SEQNO, rowData.RSRCH_TYCD, '', '', rowData.FILE_XTNS);
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheet15_1_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.06
* 3. 작성자 : 이승현
* 5. 설명 : IBSheet(관련방법론(리서치))데이터 세팅
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.06-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheet15_1_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var myRschYn = '';
if(myRschArr.includes(jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID)){
myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}else{
myRschYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet active" data-act="insert" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
myRschYn += '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite-remove btn-fav-sheet" data-act="delete" data-rptcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'" data-rschid="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'" data-rschnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TITL+'" onclick="fn_interestRsch(this)"></button>';
}
jsonObj.Data[idx].MY_RSCH_YN = myRschYn;
var fileXtns = jsonObj.Data[idx].FILE_XTNS;
if('' != fileXtns && typeof fileXtns != "undefined") fileXtns = fileXtns.toLowerCase();
if(null != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO && '' != jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != '' && typeof jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO != "undefined"){
var obj = '<button type="button" class="btn btn-download '+fileXtns+'" onclick="fn_krrchDown(\''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_RPT_ID+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DOC_MNG_NO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].DTA_SEQNO+'\', \''+jsonObj.Data[idx].RSRCH_TYCD+'\', \'\', \'\');">';
obj += '<img src="/type/common/img/contents/ico-file-'+fileXtns+'.png" alt="다운로드">';
obj += '</button>';
jsonObj.Data[idx].DOWN_ICON = obj;
}
jsonObj.Data[idx]["RSRCH_TITL#FontColor"] = "#105DA9";
}
}
}
return jsonObj;
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheetTab4_1_OnRowSearchEnd
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.25
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 재무제표 시트 로우별 이벤트
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.25-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheetTab4_1_OnRowSearchEnd(row){
var val = mySheetTab4_1.GetCellValue(row, "title");
if(val.indexOf('<strong>') > -1){
val = val.replace(/<strong>/gi, '');
val = val.replace(/<\/strong>/gi, '');
mySheetTab4_1.SetCellFontBold(row, 'title', 1);
}
val = val.replace(/&nbsp;/gi, ' ');
mySheetTab4_1.SetCellValue(row, 'title', val);
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheetTab4_2_OnRowSearchEnd
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.05.25
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 재무제표 시트 로우별 이벤트
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.05.25-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheetTab4_2_OnRowSearchEnd(row){
var val = mySheetTab4_2.GetCellValue(row, "title");
if(val.indexOf('<strong>') > -1){
val = val.replace(/<strong>/gi, '');
val = val.replace(/<\/strong>/gi, '');
mySheetTab4_2.SetCellFontBold(row, 'title', 1);
}
val = val.replace(/&nbsp;/gi, ' ');
mySheetTab4_2.SetCellValue(row, 'title', val);
}

fn_tab5Click('1');
}
function fn_tab5Click(val){
if(val == '') val = '1';
$(".subTab5 li a").removeClass('active');
$(".subTab5_"+val).addClass('active');
$(".subArea5").hide();
$(".subArea5_"+val).show();
if(val == "1"){ // 업종
if(typeof mySheetTab5_1 == 'undefined') fn_sheetTab5_1_Data();
}else{ // 계열
if(typeof mySheetTab5_2 == 'undefined') fn_sheetTab5_2_Data();
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_sheetTab5_1_Data
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업종 데이터 조회
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_sheetTab5_1_Data(){
var compCd = $("#sendForm [name=COMP_CD]").val();
fn_comm_ajax({
url : "/ajaxf/frDisclosureSvc/getCompViewDtlTpbsList.do",
data : {"COMP_CD":compCd},
dataType : "json",
success : function(data) {
if(null != data){
fn_sheetTab5_1Init(data);
}
}
});
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheetTab5_1_OnClick
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업종 시트 클릭 이벤트
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheetTab5_1_OnClick(Row, Col, Value, CellX, CellY, CellW, CellH){
if(Row == 0){
return;
}
var saveNm = mySheetTab5_1.ColSaveName(Col);
var rowData = mySheetTab5_1.GetRowData(Row);
if(saveNm == "COMP_NM"){
fn_compView(rowData.COMP_CD);
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheetTab5_2_OnClick

* 5. 설명 : 계열 시트 클릭 이벤트

function mySheetTab5_1_OnBeforeSort(col){
var rowSel = mySheetTab5_1.GetSelectRow();
var nm = mySheetTab5_1.ColSaveName(col);
fn_ibsheetHeaderSortImgInit(mySheetTab5_1);
if(nm == 'CRBN_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'CRBN_GRD', 'CRBN_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'ICR_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'ICR_GRD', 'ICR_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'IFSR_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'IFSR_GRD', 'IFSR_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'SBDB_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'SBDB_GRD', 'SBDB_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'CP_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'CP_GRD', 'CP_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'SHTRB_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'SHTRB_GRD', 'SHTRB_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'DRVT_CBNN_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'DRVT_CBNN_GRD', 'DRVT_CBNN_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'NWKN_CPTS_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab5_1, col, 'NWKN_CPTS_GRD', 'NWKN_CPTS_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheetTab5_1_OnLoadData
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업종 IBSheet 데이터 세팅전 콜백 함수
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheetTab5_1_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var myCompYn = '';
if(myCompArr.includes(jsonObj.Data[idx].COMP_CD)){
myCompYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet" data-act="insert" data-compgbn="M0101" data-compcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].COMP_CD+'" data-compnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].COMP_NM+'" onclick="fn_interestComp(this)"></button>';

* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>

function mySheetTab5_2_OnLoadData(data){
if(null != data){
var jsonObj = JSON.parse(data);
if(null != jsonObj.Data){
for(var idx=0; idx<jsonObj.Data.length; idx++){
var myCompYn = '';
if(myCompArr.includes(jsonObj.Data[idx].COMP_CD)){
myCompYn = '<button type="button" class="btn-favorite btn-fav-sheet" data-act="insert" data-compgbn="M0101" data-compcd="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].COMP_CD+'" data-compnm="'+jsonObj.Data[idx].COMP_NM+'" onclick="fn_interestComp(this)"></button>';

}else{

}

}
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_tab7Click
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업체별채권 서브 탭 클릭이벤트
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_tab7Click(val){
$(".btn-excel").show();
if(val == '') val = '1';
$(".subTab7 li a").removeClass('active');
$(".subTab7_"+val).addClass('active');
$(".subArea7").hide();
$(".subArea7_"+val).show();
if(val == "1"){ // 업체별 발행채권형황
if(typeof mySheetTab7_1 == 'undefined') fn_sheetTab7_1Init();
}else if(val == "2"){ // 업체별만기현황
$(".btn-excel").hide();
if(typeof myChart7_2_1 == 'undefined') fn_Chart7_2_1_Init();
//기간설정
var today = new Date();
var year = today.getFullYear();
var month = today.getMonth() + 1;
var day = today.getDate();
var lastDate = new Date(year, month, 0);
var lastMonth = ('0' + (lastDate.getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2);
var lastDay = ('0' + lastDate.getDate()).slice(-2);
var dateString = year + '-' + lastMonth + '-' + lastDay;
if($("#frm7_2 [name=STDT]").val() == ''){
var today = new Date();
today.setFullYear(today.getFullYear() - 1);
var year = today.getFullYear();
var month = today.getMonth() + 1;
var day = today.getDate();
var lastDate = new Date(year, month, 0);
var lastMonth = ('0' + (lastDate.getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2);
var lastDay = ('0' + lastDate.getDate()).slice(-2);
var dateString = year + '-' + lastMonth + '-' + lastDay;
$("#frm7_2 [name=STDT]").val(dateString);
}
if($("#frm7_2 [name=ENDT]").val() == ''){
var today = new Date();
today.setFullYear(today.getFullYear() + 1);
var year = today.getFullYear();
var month = today.getMonth() + 1;
var day = today.getDate();
var lastDate = new Date(year, month, 0);
var lastMonth = ('0' + (lastDate.getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2);
var lastDay = ('0' + lastDate.getDate()).slice(-2);
var dateString = year + '-' + lastMonth + '-' + lastDay;
$("#frm7_2 [name=ENDT]").val(dateString);
}
fn_Search7_2();
}else if(val == "3"){ // 업체별스프레드
if(typeof myChart7_3_1 == 'undefined') fn_Chart7_3_1_Init();
if(typeof mySheet7_3_1 == 'undefined') fn_Sheet7_3_1_Init();
//기간설정
var today = new Date();
var year = today.getFullYear();
var month = ('0' + (today.getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2);
var day = ('0' + today.getDate()).slice(-2);
var dateString = year + '-' + month + '-' + day;
if($("#frm7_3 [name=STDT]").val() == ''){
var today = new Date();
today.setMonth(today.getMonth() - 6);
var year = today.getFullYear();
var month = today.getMonth() + 1;
var day = today.getDate();
var lastDate = new Date(year, month, 0);
var lastMonth = ('0' + (lastDate.getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2);
var lastDay = ('0' + lastDate.getDate()).slice(-2);
var dateString = year + '-' + lastMonth + '-' + lastDay;
$("#frm7_3 [name=STDT]").val(dateString);
}
if($("#frm7_3 [name=ENDT]").val() == ''){
var today = new Date();
var year = today.getFullYear();
var month = ('0' + (today.getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2);
var day = ('0' + today.getDate()).slice(-2);
var dateString = year + '-' + month + '-' + day;
$("#frm7_3 [name=ENDT]").val(dateString);
}
fn_Search7_3();
}
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_sheetTab7_1_Data
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업체별 발행채권현황 리스트 데이터 조회
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_sheetTab7_1_Data(){
var compCd = $("#sendForm [name=COMP_CD]").val();
var selGbn = $("#frm7_1 [name=frm7_1_gbnSel]:checked").val();
var ajaxUrl = "/ajaxf/frDisclosureSvc/getCompViewIssueBondList.do";
if(selGbn == 'koscom'){
ajaxUrl = "/ajaxf/frDisclosureSvc/getCompViewIssueBondKoscomList.do";
}
fn_comm_ajax({
url : ajaxUrl,
data : {"COMP_CD":compCd},
dataType : "json",
success : function(data) {
$(".sheet7_1_1").hide();
$(".sheet7_1_2").hide();
$(".sheet7_1_title").text($("#frm7_1 [name=frm7_1_gbnSel]:checked").next().text());
if(null != data){
if(selGbn == 'ytm'){
var stdDt = data.stdDt;
if(null != stdDt && stdDt.length >= 8){
stdDt = stdDt.substr(0, 4) + '-' + stdDt.substr(4, 2) + '-' + stdDt.substr(6, 2);
}
$(".subTxt").text('(기준일 : ' + stdDt + ', 단위 : 억원, 억엔, 만$)');
$(".sheet7_1_1").show();
mySheetTab7_1.LoadSearchData(data.data);
}else{
$(".sheet7_1_2").show();
$(".subTxt").text('');
mySheetTab7_1_2.LoadSearchData(data.data);
}
}
}
});
}

function mySheetTab7_1_OnBeforeSort(col){
var nm = mySheetTab7_1.ColSaveName(col);
fn_ibsheetHeaderSortImgInit(mySheetTab7_1);
if(nm == 'GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab7_1, col, 'GRD', 'GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}else if(nm == 'CP_GRD'){
fn_ibSheetGradeSort(mySheetTab7_1, col, 'CP_GRD', 'CP_GRD_CD', "Y");
return false;
}
}


/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheetTab7_1_OnClick
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업체별 발행채권현황 시트 클릭 이벤트
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheetTab7_1_OnClick(Row, Col, Value, CellX, CellY, CellW, CellH){
if(Row < 2){
return;
}
var saveNm = mySheetTab7_1.ColSaveName(Col);
var rowData = mySheetTab7_1.GetRowData(Row);
if(saveNm == "BOND_NM"){
fn_bondDetail(rowData.BOND_NM, rowData.STND_CD);
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : mySheetTab7_1_2_OnClick
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업체별 발행채권현황(KOSCOM) 시트 클릭 이벤트

* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function mySheetTab7_1_2_OnClick(Row, Col, Value, CellX, CellY, CellW, CellH){
if(Row == 0){
return;
}
var saveNm = mySheetTab7_1_2.ColSaveName(Col);
var rowData = mySheetTab7_1_2.GetRowData(Row);
if(saveNm == "BOND_NM"){
fn_viewBondSpec(rowData.STND_CD);
}
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_bondDetail
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.28
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업체별 발행채권현황 - 채권상세 화면 이동

* 2022.06.28-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_bondDetail(bondNm, stndCd){
location.href = "/cms/frDisclosureCon/compViewBondDetail.do?"+$("#sendForm").serialize() + "&STND_CD=" + stndCd + "&BOND_NM=" + encodeURI(bondNm);
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_Search7_2
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.29
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 업체별 만기현황 조회
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.29-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_Search7_2(){
var compCd = $("#sendForm [name=COMP_CD]").val();
var stDt = $("#frm7_2 [name=STDT]").val();
stDt = stDt.replace(/-/gi, '');
var enDt = $("#frm7_2 [name=ENDT]").val();
enDt = enDt.replace(/-/gi, '');
var dtDvCd = $("#frm7_2 [name=DT_DVCD]").val();
if(stDt == ''){
$.alert('시작일을 입력하세요');
return;
}
if(enDt == ''){
$.alert('종료일을 입력하세요');
return;
}
if(stDt > enDt){
$.alert('시작일은 종료일보다 클 수 없습니다.');
return;
}
fn_comm_ajax({
url : "/ajaxf/frDisclosureSvc/getCompExprPresList.do",
data : {"COMP_CD":compCd, "STDT":stDt, "ENDT":enDt, "DT_DVCD":dtDvCd},
dataType : "json",
success : function(data) {
if(null != data){
var dataCnt = data.chart1.IBChart.Data.length;
if(dataCnt > 2000){
$(".subArea7_2 .no-data").show();
$(".subArea7_2 .subTxt7_2").hide();
$(".subArea7_2 .chart-wrap").hide();
$.alert("조회기간범위를 초과하였습니다.\n기간를 조정하여 다시 조회하시기 바랍니다.");
return;
}else{
if(dataCnt == 0){
$(".subArea7_2 .chart-wrap").hide();
$(".subArea7_2 .no-data").show();
$(".subArea7_2 .subTxt7_2").hide();
}else{
$(".subArea7_2 .chart-wrap").show();
$(".subArea7_2 .no-data").hide();
$(".subArea7_2 .subTxt7_2").show();
}
}
var points = dataCnt; //전체 데이터 건수를 구한다.
var iv = Math.ceil(points/6)-1;
if(iv<=0) iv = 1; //조회된 건이 너무 적은 경우
myChart7_2_1.removeAll(false);
myChart7_2_1.setOptions({
"chart": {
"type": "column"
},
"colors": [
"#2d3068",
"#e5404c",
"#f6c8ba",
"#b7b0b5",
"#2ea4a8",
"#47586f",
"#adab6e",
"#c9a9c3"
],
"plotOptions": {
"column": {
"borderRadius": 0
, "borderWidth": 1
, "dataLabels": {"enabled":false}
, "groupPadding": 0.2
},
"series": {
"dataLabels": {
"enabled": true,
},
"DashStyle": "solid"
}
},
"legend": {
"enabled": true
},
"yAxis": {
"title": {
"text": ""
}
,"Labels":{
Formatter:function(){
var thisVal = this.value;
var valArr = thisVal.toString().split('.');
valArr[0] = valArr[0].replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, ",");
return valArr.join('.');
}
}
},
"xAxis": {
"TickInterval":iv
}
});
myChart7_2_1.loadSearchData(data.chart1,{
append: true,
redraw: true
});
myChart7_2_1.draw(function(){});
}
}
});
}

/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_Search7_3
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.29

* 5. 설명 : 업체별 스프레드 조회
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.29-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_Search7_3(){
var compCd = $("#sendForm [name=COMP_CD]").val();
var stDt = $("#frm7_3 [name=STDT]").val();
stDt = stDt.replace(/-/gi, '');
var enDt = $("#frm7_3 [name=ENDT]").val();
enDt = enDt.replace(/-/gi, '');
var notchYn = $("#frm7_3 [name=NOTCH_YN]").val();
if(stDt == ''){
$.alert('시작일을 입력하세요');
return;
}
if(enDt == ''){
$.alert('종료일을 입력하세요');
return;
}
if(stDt > enDt){
$.alert('시작일은 종료일보다 클 수 없습니다.');
return;
}
var stndCd = $("#frm7_3 [name=STND_CD]").val();
var grd = $("#frm7_3 [name=GRD]").val();
var remnTrmCd = $("#frm7_3 [name=REMN_TRM_CD]").val();
fn_comm_ajax({
url : "/ajaxf/frDisclosureSvc/getCompSpreadList.do",
data : {"COMP_CD":compCd, "STDT":stDt, "ENDT":enDt, "NOTCH_YN":notchYn, "STND_CD":stndCd, "GRD":grd, "REMN_TRM_CD":remnTrmCd},
dataType : "json",
success : function(data) {
if(null != data){
var dataCnt = data.basicDataCnt;
if(dataCnt > 2000){
$(".subArea7_3 .no-data").show();
$(".subArea7_3 .chart-wrap").hide();
$.alert("조회기간범위를 초과하였습니다.\n기간를 조정하여 다시 조회하시기 바랍니다.");
return;
}else{
if(dataCnt == 0){
$(".subArea7_3 .chart-wrap").hide();
$(".subArea7_3 .no-data").show();
}else{
$(".subArea7_3 .chart-wrap").show();
$(".subArea7_3 .no-data").hide();
}
}
var points = dataCnt; //전체 데이터 건수를 구한다.
var iv = Math.ceil(points/29)-1;
if(iv<=0) iv = 1; //조회된 건이 너무 적은 경우

mySheetTab7_3_1.LoadSearchData(data.basicData);
myChart7_3_1.removeAll(false);
myChart7_3_1.setOptions({
"chart": {
"type": "line"
},
"colors": [
"#2d3068",
"#e5404c",
"#f6c8ba",
"#b7b0b5",
"#2ea4a8",
"#47586f",
"#adab6e",
"#c9a9c3"
],
"plotOptions": {
"series": {
"marker": {
"enabled": false,
"states": {
"hover": {
"enabled": false
},
"select": {
"enabled": false
}
}
},
"animation": false
}
},
"legend": {
"enabled": true
},
"tooltip":{
"enabled":false
},
"yAxis": {
"title": {
"text": ""
}
, "TickInterval": data.yTerm
},
"xAxis": {
"title": {
"text": ""
}
, "TickInterval": iv
}
});
myChart7_3_1.draw(function(){});
myChart7_3_1.loadSearchData(data.selectedChart,{
append: true,
redraw: true
});
}
}
});
}
/**
* <pre>
* 1. 함수명 : fn_viewBondSpec
* 2. 작성일 : 2022.06.29
* 3. 작성자 : 임정혁
* 5. 설명 : 채권 상세 팝업
* 수정일 – 수정자 - 수정내용
* 2022.06.29-비브이에스-최초작성
* </pre>
*/
function fn_viewBondSpec(stndCd){
$("body").css("overflow-y","hidden");
var ifrSrc = "/cms/frDisclosureCon/bondDetailPop.do?STND_CD=" + stndCd;
$('<iframe id="iframeBondPop" class="pop_iframe on" src="'+ifrSrc+'" frameborder="0" style="left: 0;border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; top: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100vh; position: fixed; z-index: 999999; backdrop-filter: blur(3px);"/>').appendTo($("body"));
}
</script>
